ytoarchitecture  \nof **insular** **cortex** in less common … Our observations reveal that the **insular** **cortex** is extremely …\n\n[Save](javascript:void\\(0\\)) [Cite](javascript:void\\(0\\)) [Cited by 152](/scholar?cites=1106328860038311160&as_sdt=400005&sciodt=0,14&hl=en) [Related articles](/scholar?q=related:-KxYkzx4Wg8J:scholar.google.com/&scioq=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14) [All 12 versions](/scholar?cluster=1106328860038311160&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)[](javascript:void\\(0\\) \"More\")[](javascript:void\\(0\\) \"Fewer\")\n\n[Create alert](/scholar_alerts?view_op=create_alert_options&hl=en&alert_query=%22insular+cortex%22++anatomy+review&alert_params=%3Fhl%3Den%26as_sdt%3D0,14)\n\n**Previous**\n\n**1**\n\n[2](/scholar?start=10&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[3](/scholar?start=20&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[4](/scholar?start=30&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[5](/scholar?start=40&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[6](/scholar?start=50&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[7](/scholar?start=60&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[8](/scholar?start=70&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[9](/scholar?start=80&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[10](/scholar?start=90&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n[**Next**](/scholar?start=10&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)\n\n**1**[2](/scholar?start=10&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)[3](/scholar?start=20&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)[4](/scholar?start=30&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)[5](/scholar?start=40&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)[6](/scholar?start=50&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)[7](/scholar?start=60&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl=en&as_sdt=0,14)[8](/scholar?start=70&q=insular+cortex+anatomy+review&hl