{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778904606133,"sessionID":"ses_1d108571bffeBfolSmUz0E2IbX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:25","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/terms/UBERON_0034891.obo","content":"[Term]\nid: UBERON:0034891\nname: insular cortex\ndef: \"A portion of the cerebral cortex folded deep within the lateral sulcus (the fissure separating the temporal lobe from the parietal and frontal lobes) within each hemisphere of the mammalian brain. It is the primary gustatory cortex and is involved in sensorimotor and somatosensory as well as socioemotional functions.\" [PMID:34033368, Wikipedia:Insular_cortex, MeSH:D000087623, https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4964-5083]\nsynonym: \"cortex of insula\" EXACT [FMA:242223]\nsynonym: \"gray matter of insula\" RELATED [FMA:242223]\nsynonym: \"ICx\" RELATED OMO:0003000 [DHBA:10288]\nsynonym: \"iNS\" BROAD OMO:0003000 [FMA:242223, FMA:CMA]\nsynonym: \"insular neocortex\" EXACT [DHBA:10288]\nproperty_value: dcterms-date \"2026-05-16T04:09:31Z\" xsd:dateTime\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3448\" xsd:anyURI\nrelationship: dc-contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4964-5083 ! Dana Gabuxda\nxref: BM:Tel-Cx-Ins\nxref: DHBA:10288\nxref: DMBA:16058\nxref: EMAPA:35432\nxref: FMA:242223\nxref: MA:0000909\nxref: SCTID:369221008\nis_a: UBERON:0016529 ! cortex of cerebral lobe\nrelationship: part_of UBERON:0002022 ! insula\n\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/terms/UBERON_0034891.obo","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"terms/UBERON_0034891.obo","time":{"start":1778904606123,"end":1778904606130}},"id":"prt_e2efa0e62001RC8MBe1Dt6WIu3","sessionID":"ses_1d108571bffeBfolSmUz0E2IbX","messageID":"msg_e2efa077c001KPLFXSa7HiYwrk"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778904615079,"sessionID":"ses_1d108571bffeBfolSmUz0E2IbX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:26","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/terms/UBERON_0013540.obo","content":"[Term]\nid: UBERON:0013540\nname: Brodmann (1909) area 9\ndef: \"A cytoarchitecturally defined portion of the frontal cortex in the brain of humans and other primates. It contributes to the dorsolateral and medial prefrontal cortex and plays a role in executive functions such as working memory, planning, inhibition, decision-making, and reasoning. Its cytoarchitecture is referred to as granular due to the concentration of granule cells in layer IV. Its internal pyramidal layer (V) is divisible into two sublayers, an outer layer 5a of densely distributed medium-size ganglion cells that partially merges with layer IV, and an inner, clearer, cell-poor layer 5b; the pyramidal cells of sublayer 3b of the external pyramidal layer (III) are smaller and sparser in distribution; the external granular layer (II) is narrow, with small numbers of sparsely distributed granule cells.\" [Wikipedia:Brodmann_area_9, https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4964-5083]\nsynonym: \"area 9 of Brodmann\" EXACT [FMA:68606]\nsynonym: \"area 9 of Brodmann (guenon)\" RELATED [NeuroNames:1024]\nsynonym: \"area 9 of Brodmann-1909\" EXACT [BIRNLEX:1740]\nsynonym: \"area frontalis granularis\" EXACT OMO:0003011 [BIRNLEX:1740, Wikipedia:Brodmann_area_9]\nsynonym: \"B09-9\" BROAD OMO:0003000 [BIRNLEX:1740, NIFSTD:SumsDB_abbrevSource]\nsynonym: \"B09-9\" EXACT [BIRNLEX:1740]\nsynonym: \"BA9\" RELATED [FMA:68606]\nsynonym: \"Brodmann (1909) area 9\" EXACT [BIRNLEX:1740]\nsynonym: \"Brodmann area 9\" EXACT [FMA:68606]\nsynonym: \"Brodmann area 9, granular frontal\" EXACT [BIRNLEX:1740]\nsynonym: \"brodmann's area 9\" RELATED [NeuroNames:1024]\nsynonym: \"granular frontal area\" EXACT [FMA:68606]\nproperty_value: dcterms-date \"2026-05-16T04:09:31Z\" xsd:dateTime\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3448\" xsd:anyURI\nrelationship: dc-contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4964-5083 ! Dana Gabuxda\nxref: BIRNLEX:1740\nxref: FMA:68606\nxref: neuronames:1024 {source=\"BIRNLEX:1740\"}\nxref: UMLS:C1272531 {source=\"BIRNLEX:1740\"}\nxref: Wikipedia:Brodmann_area_9\nis_a: UBERON:0013529 {source=\"NIFSTD\"} ! Brodmann area\nrelationship: part_of UBERON:0009834 {source=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3308-6245\"} ! dorsolateral prefrontal cortex\n\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/terms/UBERON_0013540.obo","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"terms/UBERON_0013540.obo","time":{"start":1778904615071,"end":1778904615077}},"id":"prt_e2efa25ef001XXIfzw1aN3314E","sessionID":"ses_1d108571bffeBfolSmUz0E2IbX","messageID":"msg_e2efa077c001KPLFXSa7HiYwrk"}}
